For initial setup, run the following commands from inside the project's root directory:

mkdir {hooks,merges,platforms,plugins}

cordova platform add ios

cp icons_backup/* platforms/ios/Bushido\ Cards/Resources/icons/

cp splash_backup/* platforms/ios/Bushido\ Cards/Resources/splash/

cordova plugins add com.ben2.cordova.keyboard com.lesfrancschatons.cordova.plugins.pdfreader https://github.com/ohh2ahh/AppAvailability.git de.appplant.cordova.plugin.hidden-statusbar-overlay org.apache.cordova.file org.apache.cordova.inappbrowser

Amend boolean values for settings in plugins/com.lesfrancschatons.cordova.plugins.pdfreader/src/ios/ReaderFramework/src/ReaderConstants.h